** Shiny ** 

Should you automate?
- Make a simple calculator based on this (https://xkcd.com/1205/) comic that tells the user whether they should automate a given task.
- Inputs: estimated time to do the task manually? how often will you repeat the task per X for how many years? how much time will it cost you to automate? have you done the task manually before? have you automated something similar before?

- How happy is the Bundestag (crossover with NLP)
